<Section
  id={"section-g"}
  title={"G. External Integrations"}
  themeTag={"4 kỹ thuật · phần lớn MỚI vs opencode"}
>
  <Callout type="unique">
    <Fragment is:raw>
      Khác với opencode (CLI-only), OpenHarness mở rộng agent ra ngoài terminal:
      <strong>channels</strong> (Slack/Feishu/Discord/Telegram/Matrix),
      <strong>LSP</strong> qua Python AST, <strong>Docker sandbox</strong> cho
      tool execution, và <strong>cron scheduler</strong> cho background task.
      Biến agent thành "always-on service" thay vì "tool chạy trong editor".
    </Fragment>
  </Callout>
  <Technique
    id={"t27"}
    title={"T27. Multi-channel bus (Slack/Feishu/Discord/Telegram/Matrix)"}
    tid={"G.1"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/channels/bus/queue.py</code> · <code>src/openharness/channels/impl/*</code> · <strong>Core:</strong> <code>MessageBus</code> với 2 asyncio.Queue (inbound/outbound)"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span>
      asyncio <span class="kw">from</span> dataclasses <span
      class="kw">import</span> dataclass <span class="deco">@dataclass</span>
      <span class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">ChannelMessage</span>:
      channel: str <span class="com"># "slack" | "feishu" | "discord" |
      ...</span> source_id: str <span class="com"># channel-specific thread /
      room</span> user: str text: str raw: dict <span class="com"># adapter
      payload gốc</span> <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">MessageBus</span>: <span class="str">"""Single agent, many
      channels. Inbound từ N channel → 1 queue, outbound từ agent → fan-out về
      đúng channel qua source_id."""</span> <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">__init__</span>(self): self.inbound:
      asyncio.Queue[ChannelMessage] = asyncio.Queue(maxsize=1024) self.outbound:
      asyncio.Queue[tuple[str, str, str]] = asyncio.Queue() self._channels:
      dict[str, ChannelAdapter] = {} <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">register</span>(self, name: str, adapter: ChannelAdapter):
      self._channels[name] = adapter <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">start</span>(self): tasks = [asyncio.create_task(c.run(self))
      <span class="kw">for</span> c <span class="kw">in</span>
      self._channels.values()]
      tasks.append(asyncio.create_task(self._outbound_dispatcher())) <span
      class="kw">await</span> asyncio.gather(*tasks, return_exceptions=<span
      class="kw">True</span>) <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">_outbound_dispatcher</span>(self): <span
      class="kw">while</span> <span class="kw">True</span>: channel, source_id,
      text = <span class="kw">await</span> self.outbound.get() adapter =
      self._channels.get(channel) <span class="kw">if</span> adapter: <span
      class="kw">await</span> adapter.send(source_id, text) <span class="com">#
      Feishu adapter — WebSocket long-connection với payload 40KB</span> <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">FeishuAdapter</span>(ChannelAdapter): MAX_PAYLOAD = 40_000
      <span class="com"># ~40KB per interactive card</span> <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">run</span>(self, bus:
      MessageBus): client = lark.ws.Client(app_id=..., app_secret=...,
      event_handler=<span class="kw">lambda</span> evt: self._on_event(evt,
      bus)) <span class="kw">await</span> client.start() </code></pre> <div
      class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan trọng:</strong> Đa số harness coi agent
      chỉ sống trong 1 kênh (CLI, API). MessageBus pattern cho phép <strong>một
      agent</strong> đồng thời nhận message từ Slack DM, Feishu group, Discord
      channel, Telegram bot, và Matrix room — tất cả đều được normalize thành
      <code>ChannelMessage</code>. Outbound dispatcher lo chuyện format lại (ví
      dụ: Feishu cards, Slack Block Kit, Discord embed). Đây là cơ sở cho
      <em>personal agent always-on</em> (ohmo): user ping từ bất cứ đâu, agent
      respond đúng context.</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4>
      <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span> asyncio <span
      class="kw">from</span> abc <span class="kw">import</span> ABC,
      abstractmethod <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">ChannelAdapter</span>(ABC): <span
      class="deco">@abstractmethod</span> <span class="kw">async def</span>
      <span class="fn">run</span>(self, bus): ... <span
      class="deco">@abstractmethod</span> <span class="kw">async def</span>
      <span class="fn">send</span>(self, source_id: str, text: str): ... <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">SlackAdapter</span>(ChannelAdapter): <span
      class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">__init__</span>(self, token):
      self.app = AsyncApp(token=token) self.app.event(<span
      class="str">"message"</span>)(self._on_message) <span class="kw">async
      def</span> <span class="fn">_on_message</span>(self, event, say, bus):
      <span class="kw">await</span> bus.inbound.put(ChannelMessage(
      channel=<span class="str">"slack"</span>, source_id=event[<span
      class="str">"channel"</span>], user=event[<span
      class="str">"user"</span>], text=event[<span class="str">"text"</span>],
      raw=event, )) <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">send</span>(self, source_id, text): <span
      class="kw">await</span>
      self.app.client.chat_postMessage(channel=source_id, text=text) <span
      class="com"># Dùng một agent cho Slack + Discord đồng thời</span> <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">main</span>(): bus =
      MessageBus() bus.register(<span class="str">"slack"</span>,
      SlackAdapter(token=<span class="str">"xoxb-..."</span>))
      bus.register(<span class="str">"discord"</span>,
      DiscordAdapter(token=<span class="str">"..."</span>)) <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">agent_loop</span>(): <span
      class="kw">while</span> <span class="kw">True</span>: msg = <span
      class="kw">await</span> bus.inbound.get() reply = <span
      class="kw">await</span> llm_reply(msg.text, user=msg.user) <span
      class="kw">await</span> bus.outbound.put((msg.channel, msg.source_id,
      reply)) <span class="kw">await</span> asyncio.gather(bus.start(),
      agent_loop()) </code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Single-agent, multi-channel — DRY adapter code",
        "Inbound queue có backpressure (maxsize=1024)",
        "Adapter dễ swap (dev → Slack, prod → Feishu)",
        "Channel ID theo <code>(channel, source_id)</code> giữ context thread",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Channel-specific features (rich card, reaction, ephemeral) khó trừu tượng",
        "Adapter tự xử lý rate-limit — không có central limiter",
        "State per-thread chưa tách biệt (nếu không cẩn thận, user A có thể thấy reply của user B)",
        "Outbound truncation (Feishu 40KB, Slack 40KB block) cần adapter lo",
      ]}
    />
